\c 26
\s Abantu bathi uJeremiya ufanele ukubulawa
\p
\v 1 Ekuqaleni kokubusa kukaJehoyakhimi indodana kaJosiya inkosi yakoJuda kwafika lelilizwi livela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 27.1.\x* lisithi:
\v 2 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Mana egumeni lendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*,\x + 19.14.\x* ukhulume kuyo yonke imizi yakoJuda, efikayo uku\add za\add*khonza endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, wonke amazwi engikulaya ukuthi uwakhulume kubo;\x + Hez. 3.10.\x* unganciphisi lalizwi.\x + Dute. 4.2; 12.32. Seb. 20.27.\x*
\v 3 Mhlawumbe bazalalela,\x + 36.3.\x* baphenduke ngulowo lalowo endleleni yakhe embi, ukuze ngizisole\x + 18.8; 26.13,19.\x* ngokubi ebengicabanga ukukwenza kubo\x + 36.3.\x* ngenxa yobubi bezenzo zabo.\x + 4.4.\x*
\v 4 Uzakuthi-ke kibo: Itsho njalo IN\nd kosi\nd*: Uba lingayikungilalela,\x + Levi 26.14. Dute. 28.15.\x* ukuthi lihambe ngomlayo wami engiwubeka phambi kwenu,
\v 5 ukuthi lilalele amazwi enceku zami abaprofethi\x + 25.3,4.\x* engibathume kini,\x + 25.3,4.\x* yebo ngivuka ngovivi ngi\add ba\add*thuma, kodwa kalilalelanga,\x + 25.3,4.\x*
\v 6 ngizakwenza-ke lindlu ibe njengeShilo,\x + 7.12,14; 26.9.\x* ngenze lumuzi ube yisiqalekiso kuzo zonke izizwe zomhlaba.\x + 24.9.\x*\x + 29.18.\x*
\v 7 Ngakho abapristi labaprofethi labo bonke abantu bamuzwa uJeremiya ekhuluma lamazwi endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*.\x + 23.33; 26.8.\x*
\p
\v 8 Kwathi uJeremiya eseqedile ukukhuluma konke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayi\add m\add*laye ukuthi akukhulume ebantwini bonke, abapristi labaprofethi labo bonke abantu bambamba besithi: Uzakufa lokufa!\x + 23.33; 26.8.\x*
\v 9 Kungani uprofetha ngebizo leN\nd kosi\nd* usithi: Lindlu izakuba njengeShilo,\x + 7.12,14; 26.9.\x* lomuzi lo uzakuba lunxiwa, ungabi lamhlali?\x + 4.7.\x* Bonke abantu basebembuthanela uJeremiya endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 10 Kwathi iziphathamandla zakoJuda sezizwile lezizinto, zenyuka zivela endlini yenkosi \add zafika\add* endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, zahlala emnyango wesango elitsha le\add ndlu y\add*eN\nd kosi\nd*.\x + 36.10.\x*
\v 11 Abapristi labaprofethi basebekhuluma kuzo iziphathamandla lakubo bonke abantu besithi: Umuntu lo ufanele isigwebo sokufa, ngoba uprofethe emelene lalumuzi,\x + 38.4.\x* njengoba lizwile ngendlebe zenu.
\p
\v 12 Wasekhuluma uJeremiya kuzo zonke iziphathamandla lakubo bonke abantu esithi: IN\nd kosi\nd* yangithuma ukuprofetha ngimelene lalindlu ngimelene lalumuzi wonke amazwi eliwezwileyo.
\v 13 Ngakho-ke lungisani indlela zenu lezenzo zenu,\x + 7.3.\x* lilalele ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu; khona iN\nd kosi\nd* izazisola ngobubi ebukhulume imelene lani.\x + 18.8; 26.13,19.\x*
\v 14 Kodwa mina, khangela, ngisesandleni senu;\x + 38.5. Josh. 9.25.\x* yenzani kimi njengokulungileyo lanjengokuqondileyo emehlweni enu.\x + 38.5. Josh. 9.25.\x*
\v 15 Kodwa yazini isibili ukuthi uba lingibulala, isibili lizakwehlisela igazi elingelacala phezu kwenu laphezu kwalumuzi laphezu kwabakhileyo bawo; ngoba ngeqiniso iN\nd kosi\nd* ingithume kini ukuthi ngikhulume wonke la amazwi endlebeni zenu.
\p
\v 16 Iziphathamandla labo bonke abantu basebesithi kubapristi lakubaprofethi: Lumuntu kafanele isigwebo sokufa, ngoba ukhulumile kithi ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu.
\v 17 Kwasekusukuma abanye\x + Seb. 5.34.\x* babadala belizwe,\x + 19.1.\x* bakhuluma kulo lonke ibandla labantu, besithi:
\v 18 UMika umMorashethi waprofetha ensukwini zikaHezekhiya inkosi yakoJuda,\x + Mika 1.1.\x* wakhuluma kibo bonke abantu bakoJuda esithi: Itsho njalo IN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla: IZiyoni izalinywa \add njeng\add*ensimu,\x + Mika 3.12.\x* leJerusalema ibe zinqumbi, lentaba yendlu ibe zindawo eziphakemeyo zegusu.
\v 19 UHezekhiya inkosi yakoJuda layo wonke uJuda bambulala isibili yini? Kayesabanga yini iN\nd kosi\nd*,\x + 2 Lan. 32.26.\x* wancenga ubuso beN\nd kosi\nd*, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yazisola ngokubi eyayikukhulume imelene labo?\x + 18.8; 26.13,19.\x*\x + 2 Lan. 32.26.\x*\x + Eks. 32.14. 2 Sam. 24.16.\x* Ngalokho senza ububi obukhulu simelene lemiphefumulo yethu.\x + Seb. 5.39.\x*
\p
\v 20 Kwakukhona njalo umuntu owaprofetha ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd*, uUriya indodana kaShemaya oweKiriyathi-Jeyarimi,\x + Josh. 9.17.\x* owaprofetha ngalumuzi langalelilizwe njengokwamazwi wonke kaJeremiya.
\v 21 Kwathi inkosi uJehoyakhimi\x + 26.1; 27.1.\x* lawo wonke amaqhawe akhe lazo zonke iziphathamandla zakhe besizwa amazwi akhe, inkosi yadinga ukumbulala; kwathi uUriya ekuzwa, wesaba, wabaleka, waya eGibhithe.
\v 22 Inkosi uJehoyakhimi yasithuma amadoda eGibhithe, uElinathani\x + 36.12,25. 2 Kho. 24.8.\x* indodana kaAkhibhori,\x + 2 Kho. 22.12,14.\x* la\add manye\add* amadoda kanye laye eGibhithe,
\v 23 basebemkhipha uUriya eGibhithe, bamletha enkosini uJehoyakhimi, owambulala ngenkemba,\x + 22.17. Neh. 9.26. Mat. 21.35.\x* waphosela isidumbu sakhe emangcwabeni abantwana babantu.
\p
\v 24 Kodwa isandla sikaAhikhamu\x + 2 Kho. 22.12.\x* indodana kaShafani\x + 36.10. 2 Lan. 34.8.\x* sasiloJeremiya, ukuze bangamnikeli esandleni sabantu ukuthi bambulale.